title: Full Show (Bucs beat Ravens on TNF, LeBron’s cryptic post, Dak says he’s not worried about personal stats)
description:
00:00 Bucs lose to Ravens 27-22 on TNF
25:25 LeBron makes cryptic post on Instagram after Lakers 0-4 start
55:13 Ben Simmons airballs layup in Nets OT loss to the Mavs
1:07:38 Brady has first three game losing streak since 2002. Could Tampa miss the playoffs?
1:19:57 Dak says he's not worried about personal stats
1:32:35 All-time greats Brady and LeBron are both struggling. Who is in a tougher spot this season?
1:41:42 Did Lamar make a statement about his contract situation after win over the Bucs on TNF?
1:48:21 KD is averaging career-high in points this season. Is the Nets 1-4 start more on him or his teammates?
01:53:16 Tom Brady becomes most sacked QB in NFL history
